  U7 chit8 am3 goeh8 am3-mi5, in saN e5 chhoa7 chhut-khi3 Sai3-hoa-lau5, khi3 kap lang5 chheng-siau3 sng3 hoa-tai7 , chiu7-si7 siok8 Bi2-chu e5 sin-ke3, ti7 hia soa3 hou7 lang5 chhiaN2. Thau5-ke chhio3 gi7-gi7 pan7 chit8 toh khiau-khiau, kho2-sioh hit am3 Khun-hong lioh8-a2 kam2-tioh8 bo5 sim2-mih8 kaN2 lim chiu2, chiah lim nng7 koan3 Beh8-a2-chiu2 na7-tiaN7. Na7-si7 peng5-si5 chit8 taN2 bo5 lun2--i, Ui-suh-kih, but8-lan5-ti5 koan3-goa7 ia7-si7 boe7 chui3, chheng-chiu2 lim-tit kui2-na7 koan3. Na7-si7 nng7 e5 bou2 ti7 sin-piN, koh si7 sng3 u7 tioh8 siaN5-lai7 e5 bi2-jin5, chiu7 kek an2-ni khong-khong hou7 nng7 e5 se3-i5-a2 chit8 e5 chhah chit8 peng5 ian5-lou7 san3-pou7 to3-lai5. Moa nng7 e5 se3-i5 teh kiaN5 iu5-goan5 tui3 toa7-lou7 phaiN2-se3, tui3 au7-boe2 lou7, tui3 in au7-hoe-hng5 jip8--lai5. ThiaN lang5 ti7 au7-hoe-hng5 e5 lian5-hoe-ti5 piN teh khau3. SaN e5 chiu7 houN3 ki5-sim kiaN5 tui3 hia khi3, koh si7 cha-bou2-lang5 siaN, Khun-hong sio2-khoa2 chui3-se3, chui3-se3, be7 jin7-tit siaN. Siu3-chhun chit8 e7 chiu7 chai si7 Hui7-bi2 e5 siaN, chiu7 thoa in tui3 hia khi3. Tu2-tu2 si7 Hui7-bi2 chio Sou3-lan5 khi3 lian5-hoe-ti5 piN ki5-to2. Sou3-lan5 khoaN3 lang5 lai5 kin2 chau2 khi3 bih, in long2 m7-chai. Chhun Hui7-bi2 ti7 hia, in kiaN5 oa2--lai5, Hui7-bi2 tui3 Khun-hong e5 kha ka7 i lam2-leh tit8-tit8 khau3. In-ui7 siuN7 tioh8 chheng-lian5 tong-si5 e5 thiaN3-cheng5, kin-a2-jit8 hou7 tiong7-hu hiat-kak8 e5 chhi-chham2, khau3 kau3 be7 tng2 siaN. Khun-hong toa7-siaN chhoh phaiN2-chhui3, soa3 kong2 hou7 i khau3-kau3 soe khi3. Hui7-bi2 in3 kong2 “A hu ah! Li2 kiam2 thang hiah8 nge7-sim kiam2 long2 be7 ki3-tit cha2-si5 e5 ai3-cheng5.” Khun-hong kong2 “Ai3-cheng5, na2 teh ai3-cheng5 leh, beh si2, si2 loh8-khi3, m7-bian2 teh koh kau-tiN5.” Me7 khah kin2, a2-si7 that-khi3 khah kin2, sun7 me7 e5 se3 chu7 an2-ni ka7 i that-khi3. Hui7-bi2 chu7 an2-ni tiam7-tiam7. Goan5-lai5 hit-si5 Hui7-bi2 si7 kui7 ti7 ti5-piN e5 chit8 liap8 toa7 chioh8-thau5 piN, phak ti7 chioh8-thau5 teh ki5