  Hui7-bi2 e5 it-seng sit8-chai7 chin kau3 kho2-lin5. Bo5 thiaN lau7-pe7 e5 ui5-gian5, hou7 cheng5-si sou2 tiN5, kau3 chia sit8-chai7 hoan2-hoe2 chin ti5. Thau5-khak tiaN7 chiah8 gou7-kin-ke5, hun-chhoe-thau5. Bak8-chiu-phoe5, chhui3-phoe2, toa7-thui2 tiaN7 hou7 lang5 liam3. Tin5-tiau5, koaiN2-a2-thau5, ta-ke phah, tiong7-hu phah. Se3-i5 tim3 bah-kut, bak8-he bak8-gin5, kiaN2 si2 tiong7-hu m7-tihN8. Kin-tu2 oah8 leh ia7 si7 khou2. 
  Khun-hong thiaN chui2-siaN, thom5-lom5 chit-siaN aih8 chit8 e7, chu7 an2-ni tiam7-tiam7 chai phaiN2-tai7 lah. Tioh8 kiaN kin2 hoah kiu3 lang5, si3-piN cheng7 chauh-chauh, am3-bin7-bong. AN3 loh8 khi3 sa, sa bo5. Siu3-chhun ke2 u7 sim, ke2 u7 i3, tit8-tit8 ka7 i kong2 “Mai3-noh, koaN5-koaN5--lang5, li2 koh lim-chiu2, ia7 hou7 kam2 tioh8 leh. Mai3 bak-chui2 lah, na2 chun2 li2 kong2--e5, si2 loh8-khi3 mai3 teh kau-tiN5. Ka7 i chun2 choe3 chu7-sat thiau3-chui2, kin-tu2 ia7 bo5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3. Si2 to si2-lah, kin-tu2 bin5-a2-chai3 chiah lai5 kou ia7-si7 sio-siang7.” Chong2-si7 Khun-hong kui2-hun u7 liong5-sim, to3-khi3 kin2 hoah tng5-kang Toa7-tai, kap nng7 e5 kio3-chhui3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 beh khi3 tau3 kou. Kau3 chhu3 mng5 iam2 leh bo5 poaN3 lang5 ti7-teh. Bio7-khau2 teh choe3 toa7-hi3, tai7-ke khi3 khoaN3 hi3. Khun-hong ka-ti7 giah8 chit8-ki tek-ko khi3 lian5-hoe-ti5 tit8 la7, tit8-tit8 kio3 Hui7-bi2. Bo5 siaN bo5 soeh, Siu3-chhun kap Bi2-chu choe3 in khun3, m7 chhap i. M7-na7 m7 chhap si7 tian-to3 hoaN-hi2. Sim-lai7 siuN7 kong2 gan2-tiong-teng tu5 khi3 lah. 
  Hui7-bi2 na2-li2 tu3 lang5 e7 tiau5. Chit8 e5 si7 na2-chun2 keng-koe3 ban7-li2 e5 chian3-tiuN5, leng5-cheng koan3-chian3 cheng5-tiuN5 e5 lau7 chian3-su7 hou5-li5-bu2 Siu3-chhun. Chit8 e5 si7 Sai3-hoa-lau5 e5 iau-ki . Sim2-mih8 khoan2 e5 thiam2-mi7 im5-loan7 e5 the2-thai3, si7 in sou2 koan3-si3, si7 chit8-lui2 chhou-hong3 e5 tho5-hoa. Hui7-bi2 hou7 lang5 me7 m7-kaN2 to3 me7 lang5, nng2-thou5 chhim kut8, kio3 hoat8-kui7 chiu7 hoat8-kui7, kui7-loh8 chong2-si7 ki5-to2, ki5-to2 bak8-chiu kheh-kheh, kiong2-chhiu2 aN3-thau5, tu2 hou7 lang5 tim3 ke-kut, bah-kut. Na7 siat-su2 bat sio2-khoa2 in3--lang5, chiu7 nng7 e5 khiN5 oa2 lai5 phah chit8 e5, Khun-hong teN3 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3. U7 si5 Sou3-lan5 khoaN3 liau2 be7 khat-tit oa2 lai5 ui7, kau3 boe2 Sou3-lan5 si7 tho2 phoe5-thiaN3. Sou2-i2 su7-su7 niu7, na7 phah chiaN3-peng5, oat8 to3-peng5 soa3 hou7 lang5 phah khah tit8. 
